				</section>
				<section>
					<h4>What if I am not able to claim my photos and yearbook during the dates itself?</h4>
					<p>You may still claim your yearbook until the end of the claiming period, which is still to be announced. <span class="bold">Claiming after the period has ended will be subject to disposal by the AEGIS 2017 Board.</span></p>
